  FAMOUS PEOPLE
============================================================

Name:          Confucius
Lived:         551 - -479
Nationality:   Chinese
Field:         Philosophy
Known For:     Confucianism
Contribution:  Ren, li, filial piety; still shapes East Asian society 2,500 years later
Quote:         "It does not matter how slowly you go as long as you do not stop."

Name:          Mahatma Gandhi
Lived:         1869 - 1948
Nationality:   Indian
Field:         Politics
Known For:     Non-violent independence movement
Contribution:  Led India to independence; satyagraha philosophy; influenced MLK and Mandela
Quote:         "Be the change you wish to see in the world."

Name:          Isaac Newton
Lived:         1643 - 1727
Nationality:   English
Field:         Physics/Math
Known For:     Laws of Motion, Gravity
Contribution:  Principia Mathematica; invented calculus; explained planetary motion
Quote:         "If I have seen further, it is by standing on the shoulders of giants."

